Package com.fasterxml.clustermate.service.cfg

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClusterConfig  
    DeferredOperationConfig
    Configuration container used for defining if and how certain types of operations can be deferred (that is, handled asynchronously and possibly after returning control to caller).
    LastAccessConfig
    Configuration settings for the last-access store.
    NodeConfig
    Configuration settings for a single cluster node.
    ServiceConfig
    Configuration Object that ClusterMate-based service uses: either read from a JSON or YAML file, or programmatically constructed.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    KeyRangeAllocationStrategy
    Enumeration used for distinguishing different configurations for cluster information, mainly allocation of ranges of key space for nodes.
